          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " N-type Ge detector with 100% relative efficiency",
                "located at 90 degrees with its cryostat front face 5",
                "cm from the center of the cell."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "2-HE-3",
                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.99999
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The nickel entrance foils were 1-",
                "microm in nominal thickness, glued onto the nickel",
                "foil holders. Fresh foils were used for most",
                "bombarding energies. Foil thicknesses were measured",
                "to +-1% using the 3.2-MeV alpha particles from 148Gd."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Cross sections were converted to S factors using the",
                "relation S(Ecm)=sigma(Ecm)*Ecm*exp((Eg/Ecm)**0.5),",
                "where Eg**0.5=164.13 keV**0.5."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The tabulated uncertainties in the S factors",
                "and their ratios include statistics, the +-1%",
                "variable systematic uncertainties, and the",
                "contribution of the uncertainty in the mean reaction",
                "energy Ecm-the latter is important only at the lowest",
                "bombarding energy."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
