              "free_text": [
                " Online, prompt gamma measurement. The gamma0",
                "yield was obtained by summing the counts in a",
                "background-subtracted window around the full-energy",
                "peak, and the 429-keV yield in a 7Be compound nucleus",
                "was determined by fitting the peak shape with the",
                "same function used for fitting the source lines and",
                "the 478-keV line in 7Li."
